snippet.textDisplay: "Tu jhoom" isn't an overrated saga. It's a perfect blow to the dark music of our age. It is very loud in its central theme, "every individual should regard oneself the center of the universe irrespective of what minions say". Thanks for keeping the centuries old sufical traditions alive in the age of rod carrier mullas.
